name: SLOW LIVING
description: Your time it's your valuable currency - I couldn't agree more, shame we only realize that once the time is running out, once it's too late! That's why I adore the slow living movement, because it gives me the opportunity to actually live and feel alive,  give me "time"to look within me, to breath and enjoy a cup of tea/chocolate/coffee with beloved ones💜✨🌿
